 then set aside. Clean mixing bowl."},{"content":"Place gelatine leaf in a small bowl of cold water to soak for 5 minutes."},{"content":"Place lemon juice, lemon zest, sugar and eggs in mixing bowl then heat <b>3 min\/85°C\/speed 2<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula."},{"content":"Add butter, white chocolate and squeezed-out gelatine then blend <b>5 sec\/speed 8<b>. Pour into a shallow dish, cover with cling film and refrigerate until solid. Once set, pipe or spoon into prebaked cases and decorate as desired. Serve at room temperature."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Cream can either be piped in small bulbs and decorated with chocolate shavings, or leveled off, dusted with caster sugar and caramelized with a blow torch."],"basicInfo":["medium","20m","2h 45m","8 portions"]}